<FONT COLOR="#333399" face="Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica">Something you might want to try would be The Testament of Venear quest.  I won't go over all the deteals (except be prepared for a long 6-8 hour camp in Highpass Hold), because you can get them an Allakazam's site.  I just did this quest 2 days ago with my best friend (we were both lvl 19 at the time) and we got really lucky camping the rare spawn.  We had to wait four hours to kill Dyllin Starbright the first time, but when we got back on in the morning, he popped 5 minutes later with no one waiting for him!  <smiles>  (You only need to kill him once -- we were both doing the same quest)<BR>Anyways, for a fairly easy quest, you are rewarded with a +10 Wis +10 Mana book (2nd slot only / no drop).  Hey!  Thats Uber at our level!  Anyways, good luck brother!  <IMG SRC="/boards/images/smiles/icon_smile.gif"><BR><BR>Staree Decisis<BR>Druid of the 21st Season<BR>Terris-Thule Server<BR>Spiritwalker (yes, I changed guilds) <BR><BR><font size=-1>[ This Message was edited by: Stare_Decisis on 2001-08-03 08:06 ]</font><BR><BR><font size=-1>[ This Message was edited by: Stare_Decisis on 2001-08-03 08:08 ]</font></FONT><BR></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR="#f7f5e6"><TD nowrap align="left">&nbsp;</TD><TD><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"><tr><td>&nbsp;&nbsp<a href="/boards/bb_profile.php?mode=view&user=1234"><img src="/boards/images/profile.gif" border=0 alt="View Profile of Stare_Decisis"></a>
